---
// TechOverview.astro
import TechOverviewMobile from './TechOverviewMobile.tsx';
---

<section class="relative bg-zinc-50 overflow-visible selection:bg-black selection:text-white border-t border-zinc-200 text-primary">
    
    <div class="hidden md:block py-48 px-6">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto relative z-10">
            
            <div class="mb-16 md:mb-24 text-center reveal-up">
                <span class="text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.5em] text-zinc-400 mb-6 block">/ NOSSO_PROCESSO</span>
                <h3 class="text-4xl md:text-7xl font-serif text-black leading-tight">
                    <span class="italic text-zinc-500">Ritual</span> de desenvolvimento.
                </h3>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
                
                <div class="group relative flex flex-col aspect-square border-2 border-black bg-white text-black transition-colors duration-300 hover:bg-black hover:text-white hover:border-black reveal-up rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="h-8 border-b border-black flex items-center px-4 gap-1.5 bg-zinc-100 group-hover:bg-zinc-900 group-hover:border-white transition-colors">
                        <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500"></div>
                        <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500"></div>
                        <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500"></div>
                        <span class="ml-auto font-mono text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider opacity-40">DATA_EXTRACTION.LOG</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-8 flex-1 flex flex-col">
                        <h4 class="font-mono text-xl font-bold uppercase mb-4 text-inherit">Imersão & DNA</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed opacity-70 font-sans mb-8">Extração de dados e análise de mercado para modelar o DNA da marca. Onde a estratégia encontra a viabilidade técnica.</p>
                        <div class="mt-auto pt-6 border-t border-black/10 group-hover:border-white/10 flex flex-col gap-4">
                            <div class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest">[ PHASE_01 ]</div>
                            <div class="h-4 overflow-hidden relative">
                                <span class="typewriter-text font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] font-bold opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100">[ BUSINESS_READY ]</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="group relative flex flex-col aspect-square border-2 border-black bg-white text-black transition-colors duration-300 hover:bg-black hover:text-white hover:border-black reveal-up delay-100 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="h-8 border-b border-black flex items-center px-4 gap-1.5 bg-zinc-100 group-hover:bg-zinc-900 group-hover:border-white transition-colors">
                        <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500"></div>
                        <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500"></div>
                        <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500"></div>
                        <span class="ml-auto font-mono text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider opacity-40">SYSTEM_ASSEMBLY.EXE</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-8 flex-1 flex flex-col">
                        <h4 class="font-mono text-xl font-bold uppercase mb-4 text-inherit">Criação & Core</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed opacity-70 font-sans mb-8">Desenvolvimento da identidade e arquitetura de software. Tradução do DNA em sistemas visuais e código de alta performance.</p>
                        <div class="mt-auto pt-6 border-t border-black/10 group-hover:border-white/10 flex flex-col gap-4">
                            <div class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest">[ PHASE_02 ]</div>
                            <div class="h-4 overflow-hidden relative">
                                <span class="typewriter-text font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] font-bold opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100">[ BUSINESS_READY ]</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="group relative flex flex-col aspect-square border-2 border-black bg-white text-black transition-colors duration-300 hover:bg-black hover:text-white hover:border-black reveal-up delay-200 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="h-8 border-b border-black flex items-center px-4 gap-1.5 bg-zinc-100 group-hover:bg-zinc-900 group-hover:border-white transition-colors">
                        <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500"></div>
                        <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500"></div>
                        <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500"></div>
                        <span class="ml-auto font-mono text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider opacity-40">GROWTH_DEPLOY.SYS</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-8 flex-1 flex flex-col">
                        <h4 class="font-mono text-xl font-bold uppercase mb-4 text-inherit">Expansão & Escala</h4>
                        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed opacity-70 font-sans mb-8">Lançamento assistido e monitoramento de performance. Otimização contínua através de GTM e Analytics para garantir crescimento.</p>
                        <div class="mt-auto pt-6 border-t border-black/10 group-hover:border-white/10 flex flex-col gap-4">
                            <div class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest">[ PHASE_03 ]</div>
                            <div class="h-4 overflow-hidden relative">
                                <span class="typewriter-text font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] font-bold opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100">[ BUSINESS_READY ]</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>

            <div class="mt-16 text-center opacity-10">
                <p class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.8em] text-black">TECHNICAL_SPEC_V1.1.0 // GRID_STABLE</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="md:hidden">
        <TechOverviewMobile client:only="react" />
    </div>

</section>

<style>
    @keyframes typewriter {
        from { width: 0; }
        to { width: 100%; }
    }

    .group:hover .typewriter-text {
        display: inline-block;
        white-space: nowrap;
        overflow: hidden;
        animation: typewriter 0.8s steps(20, end) forwards;
        opacity: 1 !important;
    }
</style>